This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with the task of single document summarization. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel training algorithm that uses reinforcement learning, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of evaluation metrics such as ROUGE, which is commonly used in Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper uses a neural summarization model, which is a common technique in Neural Networks (cs.NE).
